cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with hand pose estimation from images. The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The fact that it involves end-to-end training suggests that it could also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Finally, the use of 3D poses suggests that it could belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
